OL,3,CJudge tells jury to ignore 'sympathy'
OL,4,Cfor Ian Watkins killing
OL,6,FA judge has told jurors they should
OL,7,Fignore any "sympathy" for two men
OL,8,Faccused of murdering the paedophile
OL,9,FLostprophets' frontman Ian Watkins
OL,10,Fwhen considering their verdicts.
OL,12,FServing prisoners Rico Gedel and
OL,13,FSamuel Dodsworth are charged over the
OL,14,Fdeath of the disgraced singer at high-
OL,15,Fsecurity HMP Wakefield on 11 October
OL,16,Flast year.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
