CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779228661
OL,3,CJudge tells jury to ignore 'sympathy'
OL,4,Cfor Ian Watkins killing
OL,6,FLeeds Crown Court has heard Rico Gedel
OL,7,Fstabbed Watkins three times with a
OL,8,Fmakeshift knife, which he then passed
OL,9,Fto Samuel Dodsworth, who threw it in a
OL,10,Fbin.
OL,12,FGedel, 25, Dodsworth, 44, both deny
OL,13,Fmurder and possessing a knife in
OL,14,Fprison.
OL,16,FGiving his legal directions to jurors,
OL,17,Fthe judge, Mr Justice Hilliard, said
OL,18,FWatkins "had committed very serious
OL,19,Foffences, yet clearly should not have
OL,20,Flost his life in prison while serving
OL,21,Fhis sentence".
OL,26,@zD@IOU}D@MO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
