PN,36803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779228661
OL,3,CJudge tells jury to ignore 'sympathy'
OL,4,Cfor Ian Watkins killing
OL,6,F"Any sympathy you might have in those
OL,7,Fcircumstances cannot play any part in
OL,8,Fyour deliberations," he told the jury.
OL,10,FThe judge said jurors should not
OL,11,Fdecide the case based on "sympathy or
OL,12,Fdisapproval in any direction" and
OL,13,Fshould not be "concerned with the
OL,14,Fconsequences of any particular
OL,15,Fverdict".
OL,17,FHe told them they should carry out a
OL,18,F"cool, calm, careful and impartial
OL,19,Fexamination of the evidence in the
OL,20,Fcase".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@TO]sD@ZOUtD@]O]uD@OOUwD@HO]zD@
OL,26,AAOU|D@EO]
