PN,36804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779228661
OL,3,CJudge tells jury to ignore 'sympathy'
OL,4,Cfor Ian Watkins killing
OL,6,FMr Justice Hilliard said they should
OL,7,Fnot "embark on an inquiry" into
OL,8,FGedel's evidence about his time in
OL,9,Fprison, which included claims that he
OL,10,Fhated being housed with sex offenders
OL,11,Fat HMP Wakefield and had threatened to
OL,12,Fassault "any number of paedophiles" if
OL,13,Fhe was not transferred.
OL,15,FThe judge told jurors they had only
OL,16,Fheard Gedel's side of that story,
OL,17,Fadding: "You have not heard from those
OL,18,Fwho run various prisons to explain how
OL,19,Fand why they are run with the
OL,20,Fresources they have and the issues
OL,21,Fthey have to deal with."
OL,26,@oD@EOUoD@ZO]tD@IOUtD@cO]yD@IOU}D@XO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
