FL,369,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F368A1779228661
OL,3,CJudge tells jury to ignore 'sympathy'
OL,4,Cfor Ian Watkins killing
OL,6,FHe said there was no dispute that
OL,7,FGedel was guilty of at least
OL,8,Fmanslaughter, and it was agreed that a
OL,9,F"deliberate, unlawfully inflicted
OL,10,Finjury caused Ian Watkins' death".
OL,12,F"The prosecution must next prove Rico
OL,13,FGedel either intended to kill Ian
OL,14,FWatkins or cause him really serious
OL,15,Fharm when he did it," the judge said.
OL,17,FWatkins was jailed for 29 years in
OL,18,FDecember 2013, with a further six
OL,19,Fyears on licence, after admitting a
OL,20,Fstring of sex offences, including the
OL,21,Fattempted rape of a fan's baby.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@aO]tD@AOUwD@UO]
