OL,3,CJudge tells jury to ignore 'sympathy'
OL,4,Cfor Ian Watkins killing
OL,6,FGiving his closing speech to jurors on
OL,7,FMonday, prosecutor Tom Storey KC said
OL,8,FWatkins had "done nothing whatsoever
OL,9,Fto provoke this attack in the time
OL,10,Fleading up to it".
OL,12,F"However heinous his crimes were, that
OL,13,Fdid not justify his killing in any
OL,14,Fway," he said.
